name: B Tote Pitch Black
description:
The basic of totes! This stylish tote is equally durable to help transport you throughout your day.  Made from flexible, soft cowhide leather. 
Included is a Halter Strap keychain with solid brass hardware made from the same locally sourced Texas leather as the tote. You will love this bag for everyday as well as travel. Holds books, files, computers, or a wallet and keys.


Hand made in Texas
4-5 ounce leather body and foot pads
Unlined
English Bridle straps
Inside leather pocket secured with brass double cap rivets
Interior solid brass D ring
Brass feet
Keychain included
Dust bag included

Measurements:
 Length: 20.5" at top 13" at base  Width (depth): 7”  Height: 13” Handle Drop: 9.5”
